# GitHub Profile Fetcher

Get any GitHub user's profile data instantly using official API.

```bash
# Quick Start
1. pip install requests
2. python profile_fetcher.py
How It Works
Enter GitHub username

Get:

Profile picture URL

Bio & stats

Public repos count

Security First
Uses personal access token

Never hardcode tokens

Rate limit aware

Pro Tip: Create token with only read:user permission

Copy

